gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 107, Trail Blazers 95
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Trail Blazers, 107-95. LeBron James recorded 35 points, nine assists, and five rebounds for the Lakers, with Anthony Davis adding 16 points and 14 rebounds in the victory. Jerami Grant tallied 24 points, four rebounds, and three assists for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 3-0 in West Group A play, and 7-6 in the regular season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 1-2 in West Group A play, and 3-9 in the regular season.
